how can we put a mp song as ring tone in n nokia moblie here's how to an mp song as a ringtone on the n go to menu tools profiles then scroll to the profile you're currently using or the profile for which you want to set the ringtone select options personalise go to 'ringing tone line ' select options change the playlist takes some time to load about secs so you'll have to wait before the mobile displays the songs once the song list appears scroll to the song that you want to set as a ringtone and press the 'select' button change the ringtone for line in the same manner sometimes the phone might revert back to the default ringtone this is a known problem with the n make sure that you've got the n ringtones patch installed on your mobile if not download and install it from http www nokia com a hope that helps Ring tone Wireless Application Protocol Nokia Virgin Mobile Bluetooth Mozilla Firefox Danger Hiptop Windows XP Gmail MSN Messenger Mobile phone Mouse (computing) Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX 2 Verizon Wireless Mozilla Application Suite Opera (web browser) BlackBerry HTML element Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME (North America) Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX Windows Mobile Musical Instrument Digital Interface Beatmania IIDX Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME ITunes Single (music) Thomas Dolby Symbian OS Gradius Java 2 Platform, Micro Edition Blue screen of death N-Gage Screenshot DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution PlayStation Portable DDRMAX: Dance Dance Revolution DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution 7thMIX Ecco the Dolphin HyperText Transfer Protocol System 7 (Macintosh) DDRMAX: Dance Dance Revolution 6thMIX Spyware Windows 2000 AmigaOS Pump It Up I-mode Option key Uniform Resource Locator Morse Code Nokia 6620 Billboard magazine Halo 2 Control Panel (Windows) Prank flash Macromedia Flash Embedded system Short message service OpenBSD Xbox 360 Last.fm Common Unix Printing System Palm OS Windows Vista Telephone numbering plan Microsoft Windows Web crawler 2005 Philippine e